vanitygen-plusplus
------------------------------------------
A vanity address generator supporting over 100 cryptocurrencies including BTC,
ETH, LTC, TRX, and more.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libOpenCL1-2.3.5-1
  libcurl4-8.20.0-1
  libpcre1-8.45-1
  libssl3-3.5.7-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  check-0.15.2-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libOpenCL-devel-2.3.5-1
  libcurl-devel-8.20.0-1
  libpcre-devel-8.45-1
  libssl-devel-3.5.7-1
  libsubunit-devel-1.4.2-1bl2
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/10gic/vanitygen-plusplus

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/10gic/vanitygen-plusplus/archive/refs/tags/v0.3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack vanitygen-plusplus-0.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./vanitygen-plusplus-0.3.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/vanitygen-plusplus-0.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vanitygen-plusplus-0.3.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(vanitygen-plusplus)
  /usr/bin/keyconv++.exe
  /usr/bin/oclvanitygen++.exe
  /usr/bin/oclvanityminer++.exe
  /usr/bin/vanitygen++.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/vanitygen-plusplus.README
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen-plusplus/CHANGELOG
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen-plusplus/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/vanitygen-plusplus/README.md

